                    <span>This book is a fairly detailed introduction to game programming in general.  Especially if you're looking to get into the business I think this book could be a great buy.  You'll learn enough to make you dangerous by faithfully following the book.<p>It'll definitely help you fill in gaps in general game programming issues.</span>
                  
              
